title: About

Hardworking UMass Student, dedicating my life to medicine. I am on the pre-medical track, gearing up to apply to medical school. I am the founder of the professional fraternity, Mu Epsilon Delta, at UMass Amherst. To begin my medical journey, I have clocked in over five-hundred hours of EMT experience.
